    {
      "source": "First Draft Comments",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": null,
          "text": "Omar Cooper Jr from Indiana... huge part of their national championship winning team... dirty worker... blocker... selfless... compete every single snap... catches everything... runs routes extremely precisely... patient when the ball is in his hands... tough... contact balance... professional receiver... clutch... toe tapping almost gravity defying catch against Penn State... good size, good strength... starting wide receiver in the NFL... second round pick... gets you a lot of YAC... competes really hard... does all the dirty work... nobody works harder... break some tackles... slippery... get him in the third or fourth round... help your offense immensely."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
